PEREGRINE BUYS EMERGING MARKETS BUSINESS . Peregrine Investments Holdings Ltd said it had agreed to buy the emerging markets business of Sweden ' s investment banking group Carnegie AB . Carnegie Emerging Markets has a team of 26 and produces research on companies in Poland , Turkey , Israel and Greece . It is also active in Egypt , Hungary , Morocco , Romania and the Czech Republic and in time , Peregrine said it would look to expand the franchise by including Kazakhstan and Russia . " These markets are at a stage where emerging Asia was 10 years ago . The growth potential is huge , " Peregrine Securities International chief executive officer Andrew Jamieson said in a statement . - - Hong Kong News Room ( 852 ) 2843 6345 
